</p>
<p>arrest and detention of, and charges against, the secretary of a human rights non-
</p>
<p>governmental organization, coupled with searches of the NGO premises. 
</p>
<p>53. JUA 06/09/2013. Case no. BGD 10/2013. State reply: 10/09/2013. Allegations of 
</p>
