</b></p>
<p>351. The Special Rapporteur takes note of the responses of the Government of Pakistan 
</p>
<p>acknowledging receipt of his communications. He however regrets that the Government 
</p>
<p>provided no substantial response to any of the communications sent since 2011. He </p>

