</b></p>
<p>471. The Special Rapporteur calls on the Government of Ukraine to shed light on all the 
</p>
<p>concerns brought to the attention of its predecessor. In particular, a thorough and 
</p>
<p>independent investigation into allegations of human rights violations, including acts of 
</p>
<p>intimidations or harassments, committed against those exercising their rights to freedom of 
</p>
<p>peaceful assembly and of association, should be conducted; those responsible should be 
</p>
<p>held accountable; and victims should be provided with full redress. 
</p>
